<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Bolden" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Bolden,</orth> to embolden, encourage: <cit><quote>art thou thus --ed by thy distress,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.7.91" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 7, 91</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>but am --ed under your promised pardon,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 1.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 2, 55</bibl></cit>.
